org.jmisb.api.klv.st0601

Class UasDatalinkLatitude

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jmisb.api.klv.st0601.UasDatalinkLatitude
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IKlvValue, IUasDatalinkValue
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AlternatePlatformLatitude, FrameCenterLatitude, FullCornerLatitude, SensorLatitude, TargetLocationLatitude

    public abstract class UasDatalinkLatitude
extends Object
implements IUasDatalinkValue
    Abstract base class for latitude values in ST 0601.

    Used by items: 13, 23, 40, 67, 82, 84, 86, 88

    Map -(2^31-1)..(2^31-1) to +/-90. Use -(2^31) as an "error" indicator. -(2^31) = 0x80000000.

    Resolution: ~42 nano degrees.
